item.title: CVE-2023-3814|2024-08-02T07:08:50.434Z -- unknown -- advanced%20file%20manager
item.description: The Advanced File Manager WordPress plugin before 5.1.1 does not adequately authorize its usage on multisite installations, allowing site admin users to list and read arbitrary files and folders on the server.
